f=AI & Agents/gauge/custom/degradation-routing/SKILL.md · in=What happens after flag: classify signal, package evidence, route right fixer, track closure. catalog detection pointing absent agent; skill repaired connection. · p=flag doesn't reach fixer evidence intact noise. skill guarantees flag ends exactly one of: diagnosed-and-fixed, diagnosed-and-accepted, explicitly-parked (with re-check date). · wu=Any scorecard golden-run flag fires., open degradation case needs status stalled., fix applied re-measurement result in. · st:/ Protocol=CLASSIFY PACKAGE (evidence bundle) ROUTE TRACK (open case registry) CLOSE (re-measurement verdict). · in=1. Classify the flag: · in=**Operational** (cost, latency, escalations up; behavior fine) forge (technique/model diagnosis) infra angle noted ops (Engineering) platform-side., **Behavioral** (golden-set drift, success down) forge (degradation-diagnosis)., **Structural** (audit failures, skill drift anneal's audits) anneal directly., **Security-smelling** (output shapes matching aegis's detection classes, egress anomalies) quinn aegis IMMEDIATELY, outside normal loop. · in=Evidence bundle: flag line, raw metrics/run artifacts, version stamps, last relevant change (proposal ID), trailing baseline. bundle, routing bare flag actionable. One case degradation, open-case list with: id, agent, class, routed-to, opened, status, re-check date. Cases stall visible: anything past `<FILL_IN: suggested periods>` without movement escalates meta. Closure requires gauge's re-measurement showing metric back inside threshold fixer saying "fixed" necessary sufficient. Accepted degradations (forge diagnoses "this new normal, cost deliberate trade") require originating proposal become new baselines recorded, never silent. · of=Routing record case: classification, evidence bundle ref, destination, timestamps, closure verdict. Open-case list maintained append-style. · pr=flag ends somewhere purpose fixed, accepted, parked-with-a-date., Evidence travels flag; fixers never re-derive what gauge already measured., Security smells skip queue. · f=Classification ambiguous? Route forge primary alternates cc'd bundle forge's diagnosis step re-routes needed. Never park flag because classification hard. · b:with Other Skills=Consumes: agent-quality-scorecard llm-ops-basics flags; anneal's audit findings., Routes to: forge (diagnosis), anneal (skill fixes), quinn/aegis (security), ops (infra)., fleet-health-report summarizes open cases; meta receives stall escalations.